Product description:
input_text.Response A: The Wayne SWS50-12P 1/2 hp Shallow Well Jet Pump Conventional 12 gallon Tank System is a 1/2 horsepower cast iron shallow well jet pump conventional tank system with a 12 gallon horizontal tank. It has a 3/4 inch NPT discharge with a 1-1/4 inch suction, and a dual voltage (120V/240V) high efficiency square flange motor that is factory set to 240V. The pressure switch is pre-set at 30-50 PSI for automatic operation. This pump is assembled in the US with foreign and domestic parts. It is durable, with a cast iron volute and a dedicated priming port for volute filling. It can be used for wells between 0 feet and 25 feet in depth.
